Class Ambulancia

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.edu.javeriana.ambulancias.negocio.Ambulancia

  • public class Ambulancia
extends java.lang.Object
    Ambulancia.java ---------------------------------------------------------- The Ambulancia class makes a real life approximation of a real world ambulance. In the program it can be assigned to different services.
